OL,3,CMarks and Spencer to close Leicester
OL,4,Ccity store
OL,6,FMarks and Spencer has sparked fury
OL,7,Famongst shoppers after announcing the
OL,8,Fclosure of its Gallowtree Gate store
OL,9,Fin .
OL,11,FThe retail giant said decision is
OL,12,Fbecause of a shift in shopping habits
OL,13,Fand a move towards focussing on stores
OL,14,Fthat optimise customer experience.
OL,16,FIn response to the impending closure,
OL,17,FMarks and Spencer said they are
OL,18,Fcommunicating with their employees.
