OL,6,FThe company said it aims to mitigate
OL,7,Fthe impact on staff by offering
OL,8,Freassignment to other roles within the
OL,9,Fbusiness wherever possible.
OL,11,FReacting to ITV News Central, shoppers
OL,12,Fin Leicester said: "I feel really,
OL,13,Freally upset and concerned. A lot of
OL,14,Fpeople I know feel exactly the same
OL,15,Fway."
