OL,6,FAnother added: "Oh, when I heard this,
OL,7,FI was really shocked because every day
OL,8,Fwhen I finish work, I just come in,
OL,9,Fand whatever I want, I buy, because
OL,10,Fit's quality food. I'm really sad if
OL,11,Fit is closing down."
OL,13,FA third shopper said: "Well I just
OL,14,Fthink it's terrible. Everything's
OL,15,Fclosing. Leicester, we used to be
OL,16,Flovely. I don't know what's happened.
OL,17,FI really don't I really don't. But
OL,18,Fthis is sad."
