OL,6,FWhile another said it had been his
OL,7,Ffavourite place to shop in the city:
OL,8,F"This is a joke. I don't know. I don't
OL,9,Fknow anything more. I'm nearly 45
OL,10,Fyears living here. I'm always shopping
OL,11,Fhere, it's my favourite store."
OL,13,FCalum Telford, M&S regional manager,
OL,14,Fsaid: "Shopping habits are changing
OL,15,Fand our store rotation strategy is all
OL,16,Fabout making sure we have the right
OL,17,Fstores with the right space to deliver
OL,18,Fa brilliant shopping experience for
OL,19,Four customers.
