OL,6,F"That means opening stores, investing
OL,7,Fin stores but also sadly closing
OL,8,Fothers. As part of this
OL,9,Ftransformation, we have made the tough
OL,10,Fdecision to propose to close our
OL,11,FGallowtree Gate store in Leicester. We
OL,12,Fwould like to thank all our customers
OL,13,Fwho have shopped at the store over the
OL,14,Fyears.J"Our priority now is talking to
OL,15,Four colleagues about what this means
OL,16,Ffor them and should the proposals go
OL,17,Fahead, we will offer them alternative
OL,18,Froles with M&S wherever possible.
