OL,6,F"We are proud to have a strong
OL,7,Ffootprint across the East Midlands and
OL,8,Fsince 2020, have invested over
OL,9,F#20million in our stores across the
OL,10,Fregion. Our distribution centre is
OL,11,Fbased at Castle Donington, employing
OL,12,Fover 1,700 people, and in which we
OL,13,Fhave made a multi-million-pound
OL,14,Finvestment over the past six years.
OL,16,F"In addition, this year we are also
OL,17,Finvesting in our Fosse Park store in
OL,18,FLeicestershire."
