OL,6,FLeicester city centre director, Sarah
OL,7,FHarrison, said: "It's disappointing
OL,8,Fthat M&S is closing its city centre
OL,9,Fstore, but not surprising given they
OL,10,Fhave plans to close almost 70 stores
OL,11,Fand refocus their business.
OL,13,F"They've been very open with us about
OL,14,Ftheir changing business model. The
OL,15,Ffact that the store on Gallowtree
OL,16,FGate, which dates back to 1931, needs
OL,17,Fmillions of pounds of investment to
OL,18,Fmake it fit for the future has no
OL,19,Fdoubt influenced their decision.
