OL,6,F"Factors like the move to online
OL,7,Fshopping, and the rising cost of
OL,8,Fliving, mean that retailers need to
OL,9,Fadapt their offer, and city centres
OL,10,Fmust change with them ` which is why
OL,11,Fthe city council has invested so
OL,12,Fheavily in improvements to Leicester's.
OL,14,F"Looking ahead, planned investment in
OL,15,Fthe city's railway station, sporting
OL,16,Fvenues, cultural sites and
OL,17,Fattractions, including our new Roman
OL,18,FMuseum at Jewry Wall, will ensure that
OL,19,FLeicester remains an exciting
OL,20,Fdestination for visitors."
